title: NEMA Updates on Hurricane Joaquin Relief Efforts (Government of the Bahamas)
text: ( Source : Government of the Bahamas ) The National Emergency Management Agency , NEMA , held a press conference on Monday, October 12 , 2015 to update the public on the recovery efforts in the aftermath of Hurricane Joaquin. Pictured from left
